---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="P1 Express">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-4 tracking-tight">P1 Express</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-12">
        The minimalist task management method.
    </p>

    <article class="prose prose-lg prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            In a world of endless to-do lists and complex productivity systems,
            P1 Express offers a refreshing alternative: <strong
                >simplicity</strong
            >.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">The Power of One</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            The core philosophy of P1 Express is built around focusing on what
            truly matters. It's not about managing more tasks; it's about
            managing the <em>right</em> task. By stripping away the noise, P1 Express
            helps you regain clarity and control over your day.
        </p>

        <div
            class="my-12 border-l-4 border-neutral-400 dark:border-neutral-600 pl-6 py-2 italic text-xl text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300"
        >
            "Presented at the OMIMO Open Forum 2025"
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            I had the privilege of presenting P1 Express at the recent <strong
                >OMIMO Open Forum 2025</strong
            >. The reception was incredible, validating the growing need for
            minimalist tools in our increasingly complex digital lives.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">Get the App</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Experience the method yourself with the P1 Express app.
        </p>

        <a
            href="https://www.p1express.app"
            target="_blank"
            class="no-underline block border-2 border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-600 transition-all my-8"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                    <span
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                        >p1express.app</span
                    >
                    <p
                        class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 m-0 mt-2"
                    >
                        Launch the web app
                    </p>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl text-neutral-500">â†—</span>
            </div>
        </a>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">Learn More</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Dive deeper into the methodology at the official OMIMO module page:
            <a
                href="https://omimo.org/en/modules/p1.express/"
                target="_blank"
                class="font-medium hover:underline"
            >
                omimo.org/en/modules/p1.express/
            </a>
        </p>
    </article>
</Layout>
